new 27,000-square-foot building includes twice the square footage of the existing Lodge and is divided into three main sections: public spaces including a restaurant, bar, a fireside lounge, upper floor lounge and bar, private dining room, and outside lounge, a private event area with a large event room (divisible into two distinct spaces), large dressing room and meeting room, and a state-of-the-art kitchen with expanded catering services, centrally located to serve the needs for the entire facility.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2141\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/modern-lodge-event-room-040125-1100-19.jpg\" alt=\"A modern ranch lodge with a black charred cedar exterior (shou sugi ban) and a warm wood interior.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/modern-lodge-event-room-040125-1100-19.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/modern-lodge-event-room-040125-1100-19-940x1258.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/modern-lodge-event-room-040125-1100-19-800x1071.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/modern-lodge-event-room-040125-1100-19-768x1028.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/modern-lodge-event-room-040125-1100-19-1148x1536.jpg 1148w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/modern-lodge-event-room-040125-1100-19-1530x2048.jpg 1530w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1913\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/modern-lodge-event-room-040125-1100-20.jpg\" alt=\"A modern ranch lodge with a black charred cedar exterior (shou sugi ban) and a warm wood interior.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/modern-lodge-event-roo